"requested items will not expire from the cache."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/unbound.rst:113
msgid "Prefetch DNS Key Support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/manual/unbound.rst:113
msgid ""
"DNSKEY's are fetched earlier in the validation process when a Delegation "
"signer is encountered. This helps lower the latency of requests but does "
"utilize a little more CPU."
msgstr ""

